{"tid":628814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人口連續7年減少  高齡幼齡比例嚴重失衡","createTime":"2018-04-14T07:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T08:38:26.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76e7cc48c94932a57247f9a684ea30961320515a","tid":628814,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本總務省公布最新人口調查數據，指出截至去年10月，日本國內人口總數為1億2670萬6000人，和去年相比減少了27.7萬人，呈現連續7年下滑趨勢，其中65歲以上人口數突破歷史新高，達到3515萬，佔總人口的27.7%，而15歲以下人口僅1559萬，佔總人口12.3%探新低。<br />\n<br />\n據《日本放送協會》（NHK）報導，總務省公布最新人口調查數據，日本高齡化和少子化狀況越來越嚴重，本次調查發現，日本國內人口總數為1億2670萬6000人，和去年相比減少了27.7萬人，國內人口已經連續7年呈下滑趨勢，而65歲以上的高齡人口首次突破3500萬，達到了3515.2萬人新高，佔總人口的27.7%，其中75歲以上人口幾乎佔高齡人口的一半，有1748.2萬人。<br />\n<br />\n而日本15歲以下人口數量現僅有1559萬，佔總人口的12.3%，創下最低記錄，顯示日本正面臨嚴重的少子化與高齡化趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2394649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2394649&d=as0WiOeuhvz8opnM8qFyT%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e2484fa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2394649&h=bd2787bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2394649</a>"},{"pid":"33d498ffb3bc5bc73fd8c7555309a0824ed0ea59","tid":628814,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"拍咁多AV d人都唔扑野"},{"pid":"908919e6d0df3ff43b6ef2c39c4d3020098e49aa","tid":628814,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔正仆街"},{"pid":"8a7cb6e7c2bab24d3f3662c814a2735f87c57260","tid":628814,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33d498ffb3bc5bc73fd8c7555309a0824ed0ea59","tid":628814,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"拍咁多AV d人都唔扑野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:16:17.000Z","msg":"寧願打飛機"},{"pid":"706bcccb9f1729eadcd20533ace0bfd21a3415df","tid":628814,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:27:17.000Z","msg":"楢山節考囉"},{"pid":"a73a629435255e92edf85664cf60c9228bb69617","tid":628814,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T08:38:26.000Z","msg":"岩啦<br />\n<br />\n老嘢霸哂福利<br />\n後生無希望<br />\n索性攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}